of my favorite chocolate chip cookie recipes. Thanks all. Bye. Thank you, Isabel, for such an

00:15:05.239 --> 00:15:12.840
engaging presentation. Your insight into making GUI tools for data cleaning reproducible

00:15:12.840 --> 00:15:19.159
with Python has given us such a fresh perspective and something new to explore. I'll be sure to try

